(52408, 'EE25A3D3-8E09-4B95-BFEE-2D401B7758C8', 'Tonight was weird. We went to this country club for dinner with Roberta friends…they were completely uninterested in engaging us…got one question of where I’m from. It was so odd. My dad clearly doesn’t like them either….but these are the people they hang out with. And the house has had a bunch of enhancements all set up to entertain people….but Roberta doesn’t like to entertain people. It all just feels kinda empty and sad.', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-01T20:55:46.186000'),
(52409, 'EDE8BC3B-F5DD-4AA0-BC80-6C449566CE7E', 'That might be a bit of my mindset  as well. I’ve felt a bit disoriented and unfocused. I can’t listen to Ezra Klein….to upsetting and not able to read much. I’d appreciate it if you would send some love my way as well. I’m just still in a funk. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-01T20:59:03.889000'),
