(52421, 'C55BC6A6-5430-415C-AF06-95FFB22A34ED', 'So that’s my most recent  association with Israel ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T05:25:02.934516'),
(52422, '446F9E9E-8872-4C24-86CF-CCAEBE01FABB', 'You are my sunshine. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T05:25:16.570622'),
(52423, '0E52FED4-47FA-4202-84FF-862DC5BDC3AF', 'And my love ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T05:25:31.756519'),
(52424, '1598B1DA-DE0D-4CE7-9EFB-A6D8BEDA4ED7', 'And yes, you sometimes make me insane. And I️ know I️ make you insane too. And we do it because our bond, connection, love, passion is woven deep and intertwined. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T05:26:27.543861'),
(52425, '72CB02D6-4555-4F2D-8061-7D5814C9C14A', 'This week, I️ went down into such a black hole thinking our marriage was over. i have never shaken so badly before. I was living in such a panicked and sad place. I️ was a white ghost. And it’s because I️ never want to leave your side. You ARE my rock. My anchor. My conspirator. My co-pilot. My adventurer and my leveled partner all at once. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T05:29:39.976444'),
(52426, '957E0807-3ED9-4BE9-9A58-E7D061215C36', 'And I️ couldn’t imagine a life without you. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T05:29:54.788203'),
(52427, 'AA5BC040-CB60-4895-8AE1-766F117F732D', 'I️ am beyond grateful that you are willing to stretch with me. I️ know what we are doing is not conventional and that makes it hard, harder than most. But all it does, every day, is reinforce for me that you are mine. And that I️ choose you over and over again.  ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T05:31:29.578115'),
(52428, '0DE46F52-AA5F-49B0-A604-A61603AF9F5E', 'I️ love you in my bones and that’s what my body was telling me all week. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T05:35:55.464715'),
