(52447, 'F2B0F846-586B-4EAF-A55D-69D7830B24C5', 'Did you see my other texts?', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T08:43:01.913548'),
(52448, '3AE657A5-95FB-4FD6-AF86-A793A518EF3D', 'Hey love, I did. Just woke up took care of Orli and got a few minutes of exercise in.  Thank you so much for your text. It really lifted me. I’ve been in such a hole. But feeling you embracing me made me feel loved. Touch definitely a love language for me. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-02T08:45:47.244267'),
(52449, 'D4866609-A229-48EE-B6B0-263964B375B1', 'Jumping into shower for a minute ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-02T08:45:59.882603'),
(52450, '3C9A9695-7029-431D-835A-4F511F09AF41', 'Was thinking how fitting it is that on the 7th anniversary of our first date that we are going on a double date with a couple we have never met. Expanding our circle to create a love (and play) community.  I will warn them that there will be ice breakers and cake. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-02T08:53:04.814751'),
