(52452, 'DDFC5B44-FE48-43BB-9FFE-8A840E518F5B', 'Good to have both ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T08:54:01.800786'),
(52453, 'ED30E776-7BD4-4911-AAA5-E91DA88A6BD0', 'there is something that continues to nag me about last week and I️’d be grateful if you could acknowledge it here. The way you answered the phone when I️ was in garrets room was filled with hostility. I️ got super scared. My therapist and I️ talked about this a lot. And I️’d like for you to acknowledge that you being hostile to me was and is not ok. It is deeply scarring for me. I️’d really appreciate if you could talk about that. It would help me put that behind me. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T08:57:19.194590'),
(52454, '68B50769-F784-457A-B7D1-5370E2A37C45', 'Me being hostile to you was and is not okay. I completely acknowledge that. I got triggered …it pulled me back into a traumatic space being in the room with Garrett', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-02T09:00:28.365736'),
(52455, '7B0D6A46-FE99-4FFA-98F7-61EE9A39B201', 'It’s the missing part of your reflection yesterday. And it bothers me that it was missing.', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:00:37.741193'),
(52456, 'A2EAE2F5-93D1-446C-92D1-A7AE3E5DDF34', 'I hope you can understand that ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-02T09:00:45.166011'),
(52457, '846BE6A1-7EAD-45A6-9F37-C6B5215C822A', 'I️ can and there are many other ways for you to acknowledge that you are not feeling good. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:01:04.011278'),
(52458, '549FB815-DD5D-4AEA-BD4F-51ED6DC2E6AD', 'The hostility sends us both into really unproductive places ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:01:18.374923'),
(52459, 'A3DB390F-F3F1-4A59-B1CA-320260C3F3FA', 'And you owning that part is really important to me. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:01:29.583827'),
(52460, '8EFBDEC0-6569-4B23-96D1-1D5EA4FC3438', 'In the same way you don’t want me to justify my lying. I️ need you to not justify your hostility. Even though they are connected. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:02:07.470412'),
(52461, '6243EA8C-231A-44D0-9C24-34AA028881EA', 'My therapist and Priscilla have now spent a lot of time just having me practice walking away when I️ experience your hostility and I️ really need to do that. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:03:30.005746'),
(52462, '67848432-8FBE-44AC-8C98-F140045F5EDD', 'Instead, I️ freeze, get really scared. And react. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:03:51.783835'),
(52463, 'E310302E-F73B-433B-98F1-DB90C73A9117', 'So that’s my work ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:04:08.355790'),
(52464, 'F2305F4A-A2DB-459F-B57C-09CAD971258B', 'I’m not justifying at all. It was wrong and I’m sorry ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-02T09:04:11.962965'),
