(52469, 'B14B23CC-229D-483B-A65A-20E620C0A273', 'I️ know I️ wouldn’t have lied if I️ felt safe and I️ hope you know you get the best of me when you treat me with kindness and tell me how you are feeling. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:05:10.018218'),
(52470, '48A1CA48-BD17-40A6-B06F-737278E01E45', 'And I wouldn’t have been hostile if I weren’t thrown back into a traumatic space of you+Garrett unexpectedly. That was a careless move on your part ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-02T09:06:05.739999'),
(52471, 'D2EDDFC3-CB60-4E02-8FF6-AF7A34C683F7', 'Love please just be accountable for your part and don’t throw it back on me. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:06:40.613684'),
(52472, 'B1C61CBA-E2A4-4461-8CA3-1380633CA213', 'I️’be taken responsibility for my part ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:06:50.945452'),
