(52474, '0075CF0B-6C61-4065-A93F-2CE4378994B8', 'I️’m asking for you to acknowledge ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:07:11.076248'),
(52475, 'FCC61AF1-8A88-4D7F-B6F9-20DA909850B0', 'You don’t like it when I️ explain the why and I️ want you to do the same here. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:08:15.344887'),
