(52484, '0C0CA946-E12C-410F-A546-5B703F3A4B2C', 'And also, I need for you to be accountable for creating a context that to me was traumatic. The first thing I saw on that camera was you basically naked in front of the bed you just had sex in with Garrett… with a panned shot to the closet with his clothes. Should I have taken a breath and caught myself and not been reactive. Absolutely. That is on me, is my work and I apologize….you should not have to take that on and I shouldn’t not have done that.  But it didn’t come out of nowhere. And this is where I’m asking you to consider the context, and also be accountable. I know it was not intentional and that you will be more careful in the future. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-07-02T09:15:08.807290'),
(52485, 'F31E4F9D-2471-40DE-AC09-F3C11A3BCCC1', 'I️’m trying to get to a better space with you ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-07-02T09:15:12.759480'),
